10.4.19  9:49 pm   Are you waiting if so are you sad if not why did you make video called might quit

      because the first line of the song was "it's the first day of school" and that was the title, then i realized that sounds way too much like a freakin nursery rhyme, especially so soon after 'at the airport terminal' which pretty much is an actual nursery rhyme, so i looked a little further ahead to the next line which is "think i might quit", and used that instead, the other good thing about using that line for the title is it takes away any ambiguity about whether or not it says "my clit", which, strange as it may seem, had been a concern previously
